data.description: Introducing 9237 Cliffside an executive home w/sleek & contemporary design.This residence offers a striking B&W palette w/ wood accents, creating a modern sophisticated look. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a grand foyer adorned w/wood beam ceiling & pristine wood floors that extend throughout main living areas.The open-concept kitchen & family room are perfect for modern living, featuring sleek cabinetry, top-of-the-line granite & modern fixtures. The kitchen boasts a large island, floating shelves,coffee bar,wall mounted oven w/a large walk-in pantry!.Floor-to-ceiling windows flood living spaces w/natural light, offering panoramic views of lush greenery.Mudroom w/1/2 bath & cubbies for clutter free living!.Primary bathroom is a luxurious retreat w/a stand-alone tub, separate tile shower & vanities & large walk-in closet w/built-ins.Situated on a peaceful lot, this property backs up to a serene creek.Large deck & spacious backyard offer plenty of space for outdoor gatherings/activities. Tankless WH, additional storage space under the home for lawn equipment etc. TAKE OUR VIRTUAL TOUR *AGENTS SEE REMARKS*
